/** @page standard_app_mainpage Standard Application Framework

@tableofcontents

@section standard_app_mainpage_intro Introduction

`lib_standard_app` is a C framework that provides the common infrastructure
every Ledger application needs:
- An APDU I/O loop,
- Command parsing,
- Buffer and
- Integer helpers,
- BIP32 key derivation,
- Cryptographic signing wrappers,
- NVM storage, and
- Exchange-swap integration.

All public symbols that have a sensible default are declared `WEAK` so any
application can override them without relinking the whole library.

The only mandatory symbol an application must provide is:

@code{.c}
void app_main(void);
@endcode

<br>

---

